{"tid":1021570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我們沒有道德家　只有道德塔利班","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:33:19.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a101185a23f613596818c342f0d3a068d82636","tid":1021570,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chenglap/status/383793141511237632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenglap%2Fstatus%2F383793141511237632&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=7991d26c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenglap%2Fstatus%2F383793141511237632&h=4cad7c12\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chenglap/status/383793141511237632</a><br />\n<br />\n所以我們沒有道德家, 只有道德塔利班, 道德家的工作, 是將道德定義到能處理社會一些重要的課題之餘, 也把道德放鬆到讓大部份人都可以執行. 而道德塔利班, 他們則是依循教條, 不考慮有沒有執行的可行性, 也不考慮執行的效果, 只顧要求別人達成一些不合理的要求. 卻不包括自己."}]}